#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:39
msgid "Healing"
msgstr "修復ブラシモード"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:40
msgid ""
"This turns the clone brush into a healing brush: often used for removing "
"blemishes in photo retouching, and maybe blemishes in painting."
msgstr ""
"複製ブラシを修復ブラシモードに変更します。修復ブラシモードはしばしば、絵や写"
"真のレタッチ時に傷を除去するのに使用されます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:42
msgid "Only works when there's a perspective grid visible."
msgstr "パースグリッドがある場合にのみ機能します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:44
msgid "Perspective correction"
msgstr "パース補正"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:45
msgid "This feature is currently disabled."
msgstr "この機能は現在無効です。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:46
msgid "Source Point move"
msgstr "参照点を移動"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:47
msgid ""
"This will determine whether you will replicate the source point per dab or "
"per stroke. Can be useful when used with the healing brush."
msgstr ""
"描点・描線ごとに参照点を複製するかどうか、決定する機能です。修復ブラシととも"
"に使うと便利な機能です。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:48
msgid "Source Point reset before a new stroke"
msgstr "新しい描線の前に参照点をリセット"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:49
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This will reset the source point everytime you make a new stroke. So if "
#| "you were cloning a part in one stroke, having this active will allow you "
#| "to clone the same part again in a single stroke, instead of using the "
#| "source point as a permanent offset."
msgid ""
"This will reset the source point every time you make a new stroke. So if you "
"were cloning a part in one stroke, having this active will allow you to "
"clone the same part again in a single stroke, instead of using the source "
"point as a permanent offset."
msgstr ""
"新しい描線を引くたびに参照点をリセットする機能です。ある描線の一部を複製する"
"時、この機能を有効にしておくと参照点を永続的なオフセットとして使用する代わり"
"に、単一の描線内の同じ一部分を複製することができるようになります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:51
msgid ""
"Tick this to force cloning of all layers instead of just the active one."
msgstr ""
"この機能にチェックを入れると、アクティブな単一レイヤーだけでなく、全レイヤー"
"の複製が強制されます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/clone_engine.rst:53
msgid "Clone from all visible layers"
msgstr "すべての可視レイヤーから複製"

